items.name: -deep-learning-projet-Tunisian-Arabic-Hate-Speech-Detection-using-CNN-BiLSTM-
items.description: This project implements a hybrid CNN-BiLSTM deep learning model for detecting hate speech in Tunisian dialect social media content. Unlike standard Arabic, Tunisian dialect can be written in two scripts: Arabic (العربية التونسية) and Arabizi . Our model supports both formats, making it uniquely suited for real-world social media moderation.
